{"tid":856403,"cid":34,"subCid":0,"title":"(台測)侏羅紀公園1-4","createTime":"2018-10-10T14:34:59.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-10T22:14:05.000Z","uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"6dc3a65caf954cf7ed1e679db27515a2046d4824","tid":856403,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-10T14:34:59.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">睇清楚時間幾點播</span><br />\n<a href=\"http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fparadiseangel.wixsite.com%2Fthanksyour%2Fabout1&d=GMKqUHOqK0NWwf0BctgWdTCdMQr7etzq9tFbjrA%2B72k%3D&h=a5626c27\" target=\"_blank\">http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1</a> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 關ADBLOCK先睇到V台 順便開返個FLASHPLAYER<br />\n<a href=\"http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Flive.sk-knower.com%2Fuser%2Fthanksyour%3Flive%3Dvl&d=GMKqUHOqK0NWwf0BctgWdTCdMQr7etzq9tFbjrA%2B72k%3D&h=335d21be\" target=\"_blank\">http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl</a> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有OKRU睇<br />\n<a href=\"https://static.wixstatic.com/media/d8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.wixstatic.com%2Fmedia%2Fd8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg&d=GMKqUHOqK0NWwf0BctgWdTCdMQr7etzq9tFbjrA%2B72k%3D&h=5e663a23\" target=\"_blank\">https://static.wixstatic.com/media/d8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg</a> &lt;GOOGLE睇唔到解決方法好似係 BY伯爵 <br />\n<img src=\"https://n.sinaimg.cn/sinacn10/687/w450h237/20180813/cbf5-hhqtawx7713888.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fn.sinaimg.cn%2Fsinacn10%2F687%2Fw450h237%2F20180813%2Fcbf5-hhqtawx7713888.jpg&h=252a056c&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/zh/e/e7/Jurassic_Park_poster.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fzh%2Fe%2Fe7%2FJurassic_Park_poster.jpg&h=7dee0461&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n1.古生物學家阿蘭&middot;格蘭特（山姆&middot;尼爾飾）和助手兼古植物學家艾麗&middot;薩特勒（蘿拉&middot;鄧恩飾）以及混沌論數學家伊安&middot;馬爾科姆（傑夫&middot;高布倫飾）三人受國際基因科技公司（International Genetics Technologies，簡稱InGen）總裁約翰&middot;哈蒙德（李察&middot;艾登堡祿飾）所邀去位於哥斯大黎加外海的紐布拉島（Isla Nublar）上參觀遊覽一座計劃開放的名為「侏羅紀公園」的主題公園。另外，哈蒙德的孫女阿里科希絲（幼名萊克絲）和孫子提姆也被帶來參加遊園....<br />\n<br />\n2.在侏羅紀公園發生災難的4年後，John Hammond在InGen的控制權被他的姪子Peter Ludlow所奪取。與此同時，Hammond邀請Malcolm來到他家，並向Malcolm透露關於B地點就在Sorna島上。Sorna島才是真正製造恐龍的地方，而當恐龍成熟後就會被送到Nublar島上的侏羅紀公園。但因為一場颶風，造成Sorna島上的設施受到大規模破壞，而令Sorna島被廢棄和島上的恐龍要生活於野外.....<br />\n<br />\n3.一個叫艾里克&middot;科比的男孩和一位叫本&middot;希爾德布蘭德的成年人在索拿島玩帆傘運動時發生了事故，船上的人都消失了，然後船隻撞到岸上，本切斷了繩索，兩人飄到島上的樹林中後與外界失去了聯繫。<br />\n<br />\n在努布拉島上成功生還的亞倫&middot;格蘭特博士已經因其發現和經歷變成世界著名的人物，同樣死裡逃生的艾麗&middot;賽特勒博士與一位叫馬克的律師成婚並有了個兒子查理，後者稱亞倫是「恐龍男」。亞倫的助手比利相信迅猛龍比兩人所想像的還要聰明，他成功地複製出迅猛龍的喉部，可以用來發出它的聲音.....<br />\n<br />\n4.侏羅紀公園發生慘劇後22年，最初的公園創辦人約翰&middot;哈蒙德經營的『遺傳科技公司（InGen）』在瀕臨破產下被『馬斯拉尼國際企業（Masrani Corp）』收購。在企業老闆賽門&middot;馬斯拉尼的經營下，昔日公園的所在地「努布拉島」已經被企業重新建造，如今成為了一個安全指數百分之百且嶄新的恐龍主題樂園，並更名為「侏羅紀世界」。久而久之，當公園的遊客們已經開始對恐龍感到厭倦時，企業為了再度提升來遊客人數而決定創造新賣點，在生命開發實驗室的亨利&middot;吳博士在賽門的要求下創造出了一隻基因混合恐龍，命名為「帝王暴龍」.........<br />\n<br />\n12 00AM左右播了 隨時電腦大爆炸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Faddons.mozilla.org%2Fen-US%2Ffirefox%2Faddon%2Fghostery%2F&d=GMKqUHOqK0NWwf0BctgWdTCdMQr7etzq9tFbjrA%2B72k%3D&h=40b3212b\" target=\"_blank\">https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fchrome.google.com%2Fwebstore%2Fdetail%2Fghostery%2Fmlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij%3Fhl%3Dzh-TW&d=GMKqUHOqK0NWwf0BctgWdTCdMQr7etzq9tFbjrA%2B72k%3D&h=f68a5b96\" target=\"_blank\">https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW</a><br />\n裝左睇V台就唔會見左上果舊野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3c937f946e470258a28765eceb9ad8faaf8e4564","tid":856403,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-10T14:36:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7c11c19fe166811cc7757350ea10ab89fc9b3274","tid":856403,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-10T14:59:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"44d61032d89c0404e0b6b84126ea9eb153bcad72","tid":856403,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-10T15:51:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4c77913a56e66fb294a3cb9e2aed7fc127afcd9c","tid":856403,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-10T16:50:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e236068848cf2daabfd734f92ac642dc558a2100","tid":856403,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-10T18:02:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6e717aad946bb62b6503f253bcd7602e713c4ada","tid":856403,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-10T19:23:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"p